"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-46a2530ab8dd0327c4d6574442a730d1_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "162 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/550811890"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsbHn8Zmd/LMsEAMaCDg0Njg2MzkxIMe4t5gGMAA41AFAC3IJNTUwODExODkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1775470185.263224", "card_id": "Q_2016068447918900691", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 131}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我被降薪 10%，经理说降薪总比被裁员好，结果他被降薪 20%，他就不干了，说自己负担重，该如何理解？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "朋友被降薪 10%，他们领导说：公司的政策，么有办法，降薪总比被裁员好。结果第二批降薪，他被降薪 20%，他就找公司去闹，说他不能接受，每月固定支出太多"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-624b4b26b8ebb98b19746e4ee234dd81_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "161 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2016068447918900691"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIsbHn8Zmd/LMsEAMaCTExODc0NjIyNSDu19LNBjAAONgBQAxyEzIwMTYwNjg0NDc5MTg5MDA2OTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1775470185.263543", "card_id": "Q_2022276317836570866", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "微软将打造 100% 原生 Win11 应用，这一动作意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "微软 Store 和文件资源管理器合作伙伴架构师 Rudy Huyn 在社交平台确认，正在组建一支新团队负责 Windows 11 应用开发，并明确表示新应用将 100% 采用原生技术构建，不再依赖基于 Web 的组件。Huyn 发布了团队招募信息，强调产品思维和用户体验优先，不要求候选人具备 Windows 平台开发经验。有开发者询问新应用是否采用 PWA 架构，Huyn 直接否定了这一猜测，明确回应「100% 原生」。 目前微软部分所谓原生应用仍混合使用 WinUI 框架与 WebView 组件加载